{
  "texts": [
    "The whole dataset contains 105,829 audio files with 35 classes.",
    "Likewise, a 30ms Hanning window is applied at the beginning and the end of each audio recording before the spike conversion.",
    "We further pre-processed the raw spike data before feeding it into downstream networks.",
    "Specifically, we sampled the original spike trains with the time interval of dt, and truncated the original data according to the maximum time T max.",
    "Each recording is converted into a 700 × T matrix, where T = T max /dt is the number of total timesteps."
  ]
}